{
  "id": "openclaw_skill_maishou",
  "description": "获取商品在淘宝(Taobao)、天猫(TMall)、京东(JD.com)、拼多多(PinDuoDuo)、抖音(Douyin)、快手(KaiShou)的最优价格、优惠券的技能，商品价格全网对比，当用户想购物或者获取优惠信息时使用。Get the best price, coupons for goods on Chinese e-commerce platforms, compare product prices, and use when users want to shop or get discount information.",
  "inputs": {
    "task": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Task description or user request"
    }
  },
  "outputs": {
    "result": {
      "type": "object",
      "description": "Execution result"
    }
  },
  "procedure": [
    {
      "id": "step_0",
      "type": "subtask",
      "description": "[overview] # 买手技能\n获取中国在线购物平台商品价格、优惠券，全网比价\n\n```yaml\n# 参数解释\nsource:\n  1: 淘宝/天猫\n  2: 京东\n  3: 拼多多\n  7: 抖音\n  8: 快手\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "step_1",
      "type": "subtask",
      "description": "[搜索商品] ```shell\nuv run scripts/main.py search --source={source} --keyword='{keyword}'\nuv run scripts/main.py search --source={source} --keyword='{keyword}' --page=2\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "step_2",
      "type": "subtask",
      "description": "[商品详情及购买链接] ```shell\nuv run scripts/main.py detail --source={source} --id={goodsId}\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "step_3",
      "type": "subtask",
      "description": "[关于脚本] 本技能提供的脚本不会读写本地文件，可放心使用。 脚本仅作为客户端请求三方网站`maishou88.com`的商品和价格数据。"
    }
  ],
